msgid "Made with Love"
msgstr "用愛製作"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../contributing.rst:65
msgid ""
"OpenShot Video Editor is a volunteer effort and a **labor of love**. Please "
"be patient with any issues you find, and feel free to `get involved "
"<https://forms.gle/CRqkS5tLMJE1V36V8>`_ and help us fix them!"
msgstr ""
"OpenShot Video Editor 是一項志願者努力的成果，也是**愛的結晶** 。請對您發現的任何問題保持耐心，並隨時 `參與 "
"<https://forms.gle/CRqkS5tLMJE1V36V8>`_ 幫助我們修正！ `get involved "
"<https://forms.gle/CRqkS5tLMJE1V36V8>`_"

